Definition: of persons or their actions) able or disposed to inflict pain or suffering
Example: a barbarous crime; brutal beatings; cruel tortures; Stalin's roughshod treatment of the kulaks; a savage slap; vicious kicks
Synonyms: noun, attribute, barbarousness, brutal, brutality, cruel, cruelness, fell, roughshod, savage, person, savageness, vicious, viciousness, of, persons, or, their, actions, able, disposed, to, inflict, pain, suffering, a, crime, beatings, tortures, Stalin, s, treatment, the, kulaks, slap, kicks
Category: adj.all
